name: FingerPunk #022 (Jon Gray) Epic 1/1
description: Jon is an enigmatic FingerPunk, some say he is from another metaverse entirely. He is the one and only psychotherapist around to help the FingerPinks sort out their problems. The fact that he is reclusive and doesn't participate in any social circles makes him easier to trust they say. He always treats his clients with respect and compassion.
